        </a></div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="text">
                <h3 class="text-danger">Step 5: Manage Recordings</h3>
                <strong>You can always review and manage your recorded events by logging into your account at iWitness.com. Along with the video and audio which you recorded, you will see a map showing your location when the event occurred.</strong>
                <p class="tip"><strong>Tip: Recorded events are best viewed from your desk or lap-top computer.</strong></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

